00:30:40.530 --> 00:30:42.200
in fact in the first lecture.

00:30:42.200 --> 00:30:44.560
And we had the first
problem set about this.

00:30:44.560 --> 00:30:46.480
And this is sort of like
an algebraic version

00:30:46.480 --> 00:30:49.020
