00:36:24.840 --> 00:36:26.880
in class.

00:36:26.880 --> 00:36:29.520
Now, the utility
is now different.

00:36:29.520 --> 00:36:33.030
And the key difference is that
the laptop benefits are now

00:36:33.030 --> 00:36:34.540
in the future, right?

00:36:34.540 --> 00:36:38.760
So the utility of using a laptop
